title: Riz Ortolani - Cannibal Holocaust original soundtrack
description:
Riz Ortolani - Cannibal Holocaust original soundtrack

One of my absolute favorite soundtracks. Cold analogue synthezisers, weird strings and haunting drum machine sounds... Simply amazing.

The main theme at the beginning of the movie is indeed a classic and a damn great song.
